snippet.title: 《窒愛SUFFOCATE》- 前導預告
snippet.description:
由台灣獨立遊戲團隊頑皮牛NaughtyCow開發的恐怖遊戲《窒愛SUFFOCATE》，於今日首度公開遊戲內容及前導宣傳影片，預計未來將在Steam平台上市。

《窒愛SUFFOCATE》是款第一人稱單機恐怖生存遊戲，在遊玩過程中將感受到恐懼帶來的壓迫感、角色立場不同產生的隔閡衝突，與主角一同經歷這個以家為核心的驚悚故事。
Steam商店頁面:https://store.steampowered.com/app/1965270/SUFFOCATE/

《訂閱 頑皮牛頻道 及 FB粉絲專頁 以獲得遊戲最新消息!!》
FB粉絲專頁: https://www.facebook.com/NC.HorrorGame
X粉絲專頁: https://x.com/NaughtyCowGame
Discord: https://discord.gg/P2vEnBYkRA
聯絡信箱: naughtycow.game@gmail.com

《SUFFOCATE》is a PC horror game developed by NaughtyCow , the teaser trailer released for the first time today.  The game will be released on steam soon.

《SUFFOCATE》is a first person single-player horror game. 
Feel the pressure and the conflict between characters , experience this story about a broken family.
Steam Page:https://store.steampowered.com/app/1965270/SUFFOCATE/

Subscribe NaughtyCow and our FB fanpage for further news!!
Facebook:  https://www.facebook.com/NC.HorrorGame
Contact us:  naughtycow.game@gmail.com
